&lt;p&gt;Is there any workaround to forcing a global constructor autowire with AnnotationConfigApplicationContext?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="54459" author="david_syer" created="Wed, 9 Jun 2010 17:10:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The only workaround I know is to explicitly register the bean definitions yourself.  At least that doesn&apos;t infect the constructors: it just requires a special component that does the registration.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
